➜沃森生物“贱卖”含宫颈癌疫苗资产被问询，公司回应：不卖了
http://www.sohu.com/a/436808327_161795	34592
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
